des:
Hey, Greetings!!

This skill "Maths Table Calculator" is designed primarily for kids. This skill will help the user to calculate tables of zero to Infinity. 

*How does this skill work?
=) So, Basically user says he wants to find tables of 2. So, Alexa will respond tables of 2 like 2 into 0 is 0, 2 into 1 is 2,2 into 2 is 4........
In this way, Alexa will respond. It is simple to use and efficiently designed.
